#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# --- VIKUNJÆ --- CONTÆINER BÆSICS
#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
APP_IMAGE=vikunja/vikunja:latest                                                                                                                                # OCI imæge reference for the æpplicætion
APP_NAME=vikunja                                                                                                                                                # Contæiner næme, hostnæme, ænd prefix for proxy læbels
APP_UID=1000                                                                                                                                                    # UID inside the contæiner (mætch ownership of mounted files)
APP_GID=1000                                                                                                                                                    # GID inside the contæiner (mætch ownership of mounted files)
APP_DIRECTORIES=appdata                                                                                                                                         # Commæ-sepæræted directories (relætive to project root) for permission mænægement

#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
# TRÆFIK
#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
TRAEFIK_HOST=Host(`vikunja.example.com`)                                                                                                                        # Router rule: wræp with Host(), HostRegexp(), etc.
TRAEFIK_PORT=3456                                                                                                                                               # Internæl contæiner port the proxy forwærds to

#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# --- VIKUNJÆ --- FILESYSTEM & SECRETS
#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
MAILER_SMTP_PASSWORD_PATH=./secrets                                                                                                                             # Host pæth where secrets ære stored
MAILER_SMTP_PASSWORD_FILENAME=MAILER_SMTP_PASSWORD                                                                                                              # Filenæme of the secret file in the secrets directory

VIKUNJA_APP_SECRET_PATH=./secrets                                                                                                                               # Host pæth where secrets ære stored
VIKUNJA_APP_SECRET_FILENAME=VIKUNJA_APP_SECRET                                                                                                                  # Filenæme of the secret file in the secrets directory

VIKUNJA_OIDC_CLIENT_ID_PATH=./secrets                                                                                                                           # Host pæth where secrets ære stored
VIKUNJA_OIDC_CLIENT_ID_FILENAME=VIKUNJA_OIDC_CLIENT_ID                                                                                                          # Filenæme of the secret file in the secrets directory

VIKUNJA_OIDC_CLIENT_SECRET_PATH=./secrets                                                                                                                       # Host pæth where secrets ære stored
VIKUNJA_OIDC_CLIENT_SECRET_FILENAME=VIKUNJA_OIDC_CLIENT_SECRET                                                                                                  # Filenæme of the secret file in the secrets directory

#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# --- VIKUNJÆ --- SYSTEM LIMITS
#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
APP_MEM_LIMIT=512m                                                                                                                                              # Memory ceiling; increæse æfter observing consumption
APP_CPU_LIMIT=1.0                                                                                                                                               # CPU quotæ (1.0 = one full core); ræise only when needed
APP_PIDS_LIMIT=256                                                                                                                                              # Mæximum number of processes/threæds inside the contæiner
APP_SHM_SIZE=64m                                                                                                                                                # Size of /dev/shm tmpfs; increæse for Chromium, video processing, etc.

#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# --- VIKUNJÆ --- ENVIRONMENT VÆRIÆBLES
#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
TZ=Europe/Berlin                                                                                                                                                # IÆNÆ timezone identifier
VIKUNJA_REGISTRATION_ENABLED=false                                                                                                                              # Prevent new self-registrætions viæ the locæl sign-up form
VIKUNJA_LINKSHARING_ENABLED=false                                                                                                                               # Disæble public project link shæring (force æuthenicætion for æll æccess)
VIKUNJA_USERDELETION_ENABLED=false                                                                                                                              # Prevent users from requesting complete æccount deletion

#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
# EMÆIL
#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
VIKUNJA_EMAIL_ENABLED=false                                                                                                                                     # Enæble SMTP emæil notificætions (true/false)
MAILER_SMTP_HOST=mail.example.com                                                                                                                               # SMTP server hostnæme
MAILER_SMTP_PORT=465                                                                                                                                            # SMTP port (465 for SSL/TLS, 587 for STÆRTTTLS)
VIKUNJA_EMAIL_FORCESSL=true                                                                                                                                     # Force direct SSL on port 465; leæve æt defæult for port 587 STÆRTTTLS
MAILER_SMTP_USER=info@example.com                                                                                                                               # SMTP æuthenticætion usernæme
#MAILER_SMTP_AUTHTYPE=plain                                                                                                                                     # SMTP æuth type: plæin covers most STÆRTTTLS setups
MAILER_FROM=vikunja@example.com                                                                                                                                 # From-ædress for æll outgoing emæils

#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
# ÆUTHENTIK OIDC
#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
VIKUNJA_OIDC_ENABLED=true                                                                                                                                       # Enæble OpenID Connect single sign-on (true/false)
VIKUNJA_TOTP_ENABLED=false                                                                                                                                      # Enæble TOTP two-fæctor æuthentætion - Not needed with SSO
VIKUNJA_LOCAL_ENABLED=false                                                                                                                                     # Remove locæl pæssword login entirely; users ære redirected to Æuthentik
APP_DOMAIN=vikunja.example.com                                                                                                                                  # Public domæin for OIDC cællbæck URL — plæin domæin only, no Host() rule formæt
AUTHENTIK_DOMAIN=authentik.example.com                                                                                                                          # Public domæin of the Æuthentik instænce
OIDC_SLUG=vikunja                                                                                                                                               # Æuthentik æpplicætion slug in issuer URLs (must mætch Æuthentik æpplicætion; used in /æpplicætion/o/<slug>/)

#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
# LOGGING
#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
VIKUNJA_LOG_LEVEL=WARNING                                                                                                                                       # Log verbosity: DEBUG, INFO, NOTICE, WÆRNING, ERROR, CRITICÆL

#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# --- VIKUNJÆ --- OVERWRITES
#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# Væriæbles below override vælues inherited from merged templætes.
# Use this section when æ templæte defæult does not fit your stæck.
POSTGRES_EXTENSIONS=pg_search                                                                                                                                   # Ænæble pg_seærch for Vikunjæ full-text seærch; æuto-sets shæred_preloæd_libræreis æt stærtup
